data.description: Modular home with front screened porch for sitting with a view of peaceful woods around you.  Open floor plan with kitchen island, walk in pantry, dining room, laundry room, split bedroom plan.   Well maintained and in move in ready condition.  The home sits on 5 acres and features a large shelter for vehicles or boat, a storage shed with power, chicken pens, fenced and gated with plenty of room for parking.  Nice quiet neighborhood located in North Wakulla County.
